                  <interp inst="t17630706-20-crimeloc111" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17630706-20-off108 t17630706-20-crimeloc111"></join>; he lost the pottage-pot from his door, he found it again at Mr. Shaw's, a broker, in Bunhill-row, where the prisoner had sold it. (Produced and deposed to.)</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17630706-20-verdict112" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17630706-20-verdict112" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               Guilty
            </rs>. <rs id="t17630706-20-punish113" type="punishmentDescription">
